cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "sitemapr: Parse and Validate XML Sitemaps"
version: 0.0.0.9000
abstract: >-
  A deterministic toolkit for reading and validating XML, text, and index
  sitemaps against the Sitemap Protocol 0.9 and related W3C and RFC standards.
  It parses sitemap sources into tidy tibbles, expands sitemap indexes, and
  reports schema and protocol findings with stable, reproducible output.
authors:
